bt, wasn't enough.<br />Our land has astonishing atlantic landscapes, towering limestone peaks, deep beech forests, a real natural paradise. It's also very interesting for its cultural heritage, partly celtic.<br />I hope you can come and visit again, more for pleasure than for work, I'm sure you'd find some good inspiration for your art.<br />Keep the nice work, George, and thanks!<br /><br />Alex<br />","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"July 23 2012, 22:40:34 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Aviles","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/alexastur","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Alex Sebastian","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_1317986","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=51379905&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Alex Sebastian","ctime_ts":1343083234,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/117522966/50009986","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16245578#t16245578","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16245578#t16245578","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16245578#t16245578","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_1235027","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://profiles.google.com/116424516199333884439","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":16245578,"talkid":63459,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16245578#t16245578","upictitle":"Ally Fell: pic#117522966","article":"Ahhhhh . . . wishing I could be in Spain now instead of having to wait till next year, when there will be no ben