gs with lyrics in your books, or even new songs?  I understand if you would lump new lyrics with fanfic, and that is why I'm wanting your perspective, and would not proceed without permission. Currently, I'm working on some of the song of John Dowland(English lutenist) on my mandolin. <br /><br />Thank you for your time,<br /><br />Byron Grimes","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"July 28 2012, 20:38:00 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"songs","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/byron.grimes.58","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Byron Grimes","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_1325519","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=51482705&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Byron Grimes","ctime_ts":1343507880,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/47030530/1050519","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16256842#t16256842","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16256842#t16256842","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16256842#t16256842","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"silverjaime","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://silverjaime.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":16256842,"talkid":63503,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/285514.html?thread=16256842#t16256842","upictitle":"SilverJaime: James closeup","article":"And indeed, there SHOULD be endless copies of your books!! ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"July 31 2012, 07:34:17 UTC","massactio